title: Windows 8.1 Pro with Update (x64) 16.08.16 6.3.9600 [Ru/En]
description:
Windows 8.1 Pro with Update (x64) 16.08.16 6.3.9600 [En/Ru]

Architect:- 64bit
Size:- 3.15gb
Language: English/Russian
Treatment: use KMSAuto Lite 1.2.8 for activation


Based on original MSDN iso. Integrated English and Russian language + all updates up to 16th August 2016. 

Features:

- Integrated all updates up to 16.06.2016 (except "problematic":KB3044374,KB3046480,KB3080149,KB3172614,KB2967917,KB2976978);
- Integrated NET Framework 3.5 (includes .NET 2.0 and 3.0);
- Integrated English and Russian language packs;
- Cleaned up following folders for reduced size: WinSxSBackup, WinSxSManifestCache and WinSxSTemp;
- By default shows hidden files and folders.
- By default show files extensions. 
- UAC is turned off by default.
- Integrated Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributable 2005-2015 (x86 and x64)
- Integrated Google Chrome
- Integrated StartIsback+
- Integrated WinRar x64
